text: Sweeping views of the Olympic Mountains, Burrows Island, Allan Island, and Burrows Bay! Almost 3 and a half acres; neighboring parcel to the north also for sale. Single story, 2 bedroom, 1 bath home. Excellent for investors or anyone looking to gain some sweat equity! Great location, close to dining, schools and the hospital.

Whether you're enjoying the panoramic views from the dock or immersing yourself in the luxury of the well-appointed interiors, this Shelter Bay gem promises a lifestyle of tranquility and refinement. Leased land - amenities include clubhouse, sports courts, beach access & more.

Experience the epitome of waterfront living with the luxury of mooring your boat right in your backyard, courtesy of your very own double-sided 50' dock! Located in the delightful marine community of Skyline, find this wonderful rambler offering glistening views of the channel & breathtaking sunsets! Enter to discover an expansive, bright, open design, w/vaulted cedar ceilings. A home and property you have been waiting for with features you will love! Just outside of town on a private lane you will be greeted by big, tall trees will lead you to this home. A large driveway opens up to this beautiful home and shop. The property is very private and gets lots of sunshine. This well-kept home features 1712 sq ft of total living space, formal living and dining rooms, family room with fireplace off the kitchen, 3 bd and 2 full baths. Large covered concrete patio to enjoy off kitchen. Enjoy a fantastic view of the property from every room. The detached shop is 30x36, over 1080 sq ft of open area with built in work area.

Escape to panoramic vistas of Burrows Bay and surrounding islands from this modern sanctuary. With the opportunity to own your own home and the convenience of space rent, this home offers a unique living experience. Plus, water, sewer, and garbage are included in the space rent, making budgeting a breeze. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this home your own!

Stunning Lake Cavanaugh log home with 120' of lakefront and panoramic views of the islands and glaciers. This home offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort & natural beauty. Newly rebuilt dock with boat lift. Kitchen with walk-pantry, new propane cooktop/oven/fan. Living room has huge rock fireplace, french doors that open to party size deck for entertaining. Main floor primary with newly added 3/4 bath, remodeled 3/4 bath to accommodate guests. Upper level has 2 fully furnished rooms that offer versatility as extra sleeping, office, game room. Lower level has second bedroom with full bath, large rec room with sleeping space, more storage and 600+ bottle wine cellar. Furnished and move in ready for the summer. Detached 1 car garage.

Escape to your own private oasis on the Skagit River! This stunning 1.5 Acre park-like property is perched on a high bank, safely out of the flood zone. Enjoy the peace and tranquility as you relax and unwind in this beautiful natural setting. This land comes with a spacious shop, ample storage and workspace with all of the additional outbuildings. Large, well maintained fenced garden to keep out all the friendly animal neighbors. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a slice of paradise perfect for your vacation retreat.

The spacious kitchen features granite countertops, newer dishwasher/micro, ample storage, eating bar, & pantry area. The large open living space flows into dining area, leading to private backyard & patio. Imagine relaxing in the hot tub under the gazebo, surrounded by nature's beauty. Skyline Marina is the gateway to San Juan Islands with the shortest run into the islands of any marina. You will find restrooms, showers, laundry facilities, groceries, ice and ample parking. Spacious tasteful two story home has major updates including new roof, quality flooring throughout, interior paint, and furnace/heat pump providing air conditioning for hot summer days. King size master bedroom has ensuite bath with soaking tub, and large walk-in closet with new upscale closet organizer. All 3 bathrooms have been updated. Close to shopping, restaurants & freeway.

So much potential to bring your touches & make this home shine. The lot is level & cleared, lots of room to build a shop or park an RV. Great location, walk to school, (Bayview K-8th), convenient to I-5 & out of flood plain.

Five minutes to the up and coming town of Marblemount, the gateway to the North Cascade National Park, and the wild and scenic Skagit River. A must-see for any outdoor enthusiast!

neighborhoods: South Kincaid, Historic Downtown Mount Vernon

text: Welcome to Garden Meadows in Sedro Woolley! A 2-story open concept home w/ 4 bedrooms, office & 2.5 baths. You'll love the LVP flooring & natural gas fireplace. Breathtaking Northwest & sunset views. 8, 712 SF Main Residence features 5 BR's, each w/an ensuite bathroom. Chefs kitchen for the absolute finest culinary experience.
